items.headline: Welcome to Fuel Wikia
items.desc: The Fuel Wikia is a community site dedicated to the 2009 driving / exploration game "Fuel" developed by Asobo Studio. If you are a fan of this game, or even if you're just curious about it, then this is the place for you! Come explore our content and help us expand this database... or join us in discussion about the vehicles, the gameplay, or the game in general. All are welcome!
